  <p style="margin-top:1.5rem">
    <strong>Caveat:</strong> This demo accesses Lit's private <code>_$startNode</code> and
    <code>_$endNode</code> fields. In a real implementation, Lit would expose a public API
    for inserting fragments into a <code>ChildPart</code>.
